<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣١٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَاعَنَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بَيْنَ رَجُلٍ وَامْرَأَةٍ مِنَ الْأَنْصَارِ وَفَرَّقَ بَيْنَهُمَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>